title: Can you Support a Trump Supporter
itunes:title: Can you Support a Trump Supporter
description:
Today on the show it was only right to have Jadakiss and Fabolous to call in and speak about their versus battle they will be doing later on today. Also, we opened up the phone lines to see if our listeners would still stay friends with someone that is a Trump supporter after Lil Jay from Crime Mobb announced he is a Trump supporter. Moreover, the petty party leader Charlamagne was not in today for he is celebrating his birthday so instead we had listeners call in to nominate their donkey of the day!
